*********************** Routes for RestApi *************************
====================================================================

1.searchByName
GET- http://localhost/root/RestApi-php/api/searchByName.php?name=jack

2.Fetch single record
POST-http://localhost/root/RestApi-php/api/single-student.php
[raw]Body: {student_id:1}F

3.create
POST-http://localhost/root/RestApi-php/api/create.php
[raw]Body: {
			"name":"Rose Jackson",
    		"email":"Jackson@example.com",
	     	"mobile":"7221109888"
	     }
4.delete
GET- http://localhost/root/RestApi-php/api/delete.php?students_id=12

5.single-student-byGetMethod
GET- http://localhost/root/RestApi-php/api/single-student-byGetMethod.php?students_id=5
[Query Params] {key:students_id,value:5}

6.List All
GET - http://localhost/root/RestApi-php/api/list-all.php

7.update
POST - http://localhost/root/RestApi-php/api/update.php
RAW->body:
{
    "name":"John Smith",
    "email":"john_smith@example.com",
    "mobile":"91021119991",
    "students_id":5
}